{"tid":2335295,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府擬禁台港大學合作 陸委會：中共、港府從不檢討為何失民心","createTime":"2020-12-21T18:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T03:58:43.000Z","uid":207846,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"77d09685f81b73e4a111283159b8b61879b850c4","tid":2335295,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:33:47.000Z","msg":"香港實施港版國安法後，拉高了緊張情勢，也讓來台唸書的港生大幅增加。現在有消息指出，為了不讓港生受到台灣的政治影響，香港政府打算禁止台、港大學合作。銅鑼灣書店老闆林榮基也認為，這很有可能。陸委會則表示，中共和港府從不檢討為何失去民心，也批評中共強加中共黨國教育，只會引發更多反感還有抗爭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/505326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F505326&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=6c1f7f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/505326</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1420382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1420382&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FdfEBUFsnbtb5M0%2Bd5EIgxU%3D&h=909a5d4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1420382&h=aba68ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1420382</a><br />\n兩岸人士透露，從可靠情資顯示，港府有意要求香港的大學中斷與台灣各大學的交流合作，因香港當局認為港生在台受民進黨政府煽動影響，回港從事反政府等政治活動。"},{"pid":"4c768c4a851f13f0e6e6b1d1075ee383a534d063","tid":2335295,"uid":347497,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"檢討過了，結論係民心唔重要"},{"pid":"597d16ece0eab03bb60d3b5a5df22d3083d1f4fe","tid":2335295,"uid":92188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"佢都戇鳩21世紀佢以為可以封鎖到咩"},{"pid":"b697f1406a36b396d9547669184fcaf8309f30fe","tid":2335295,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"On99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fad2356af362c497b6